name: My Race Against Time
description: My new NFT, inspired by my own race against time, if I don't have a kidney transplant soon, my life will practically turn off. However I am optimistic and very positive that I will reach the goal. I thank everyone for their support in the acquisition of my works. Visit my profile, there are more NFTs on it. AlfonsoJ.
